translations: n.副本，[印刷]复制品（duplicate 的复数形式）；多重记录；倍增

sentences.sentence: I refer to the thousands of pottery vessels and ancient lamps that are essentially duplicates of one another.
sentences.translation: 我指的是成千上万的陶器器皿和古老的灯，它们基本上是一个接一个的复制品。

sentences.sentence: These records are called suspect duplicates.
sentences.translation: 这些记录称为可疑副本。
